</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the left hand winder assembly. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">See : 
<xref keyref="19DISA016" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-F8FD5418-11AE-468B-8C1A-CA4E0023C5B7.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 19 How to remove the left hand winder drive assembly?>19 How to remove the left hand winder drive assembly</xref>. 
</p></li></ol></prereq><section id="GUID-E4895B67-7FC1-4974-A5C8-D34725505879" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Required tools</title><ul id="UL_A32A562039FB485780CA65B069EE577C" class="- topic/ul "><li id="LI_55373F9DAE644089ABBC568E03CDE4FC" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Screwdriver Torx T20. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Socket wrench 7 mm. 
</p></li></ul></section><section id="GUID-EC9C24D5-D455-4022-B616-D7FEF4DE0A1A" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Illustration</title><fig id="GUID-F1AA2168-2D0F-42B8-8939-EDF3956155EB" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-30B885BB-0629-4AB7-BA78-28CC208E1281-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-30B885BB-0629-4AB7-BA78-28CC208E1281-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-96C04C61-CC68-4A88-A06B-0C6132651872" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-ED614EFF-4A0C-42B8-8555-49650FEB7B46-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-ED614EFF-4A0C-42B8-8555-49650FEB7B46-low.png"/></fig></section><section id="SECTION_DACE34B3D19943EF85419C55E3285A63" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">How to remove</title><table pgwide="1" id="TABLE_3B033A86E1FC4B4DB8FE5EB93DCAF4AF" class="- topic/table "><tgroup align="left" outputclass="step" cols="3" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="10*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="50*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col3" colnum="3" colwidth="40*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead valign="top" class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Step 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remarks 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody valign="top" class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">1 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Place the unit on a table. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> 
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">2 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Disconnect the motor encoder connector. 
</p><note type="important" id="GUID-6D26D1CC-89E0-4246-A8DA-1BB9BB916EDB" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">DO not remove the motor encoder. It will break. 
</p></note></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-055685CA-1C16-442F-8351-44EC961DA52A" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-FDFB4580-B838-414A-9014-EFDDF39290FC-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-FDFB4580-B838-414A-9014-EFDDF39290FC-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-F0F16373-19B4-4215-8DB4-0C7DDC0E1E2D" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-3BB01658-A448-49F2-AB92-270E3C9083B2-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-3BB01658-A448-49F2-AB92-270E3C9083B2-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">3 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the inside cover (3 screws). 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-CA330B57-C5AF-409D-A82A-966A4486B19E" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-4A826B5B-3643-457C-8773-FBC1AF0DE44A-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-4A826B5B-3643-457C-8773-FBC1AF0DE44A-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">4 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Remove the screw of the cover. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-27741F35-F9DF-423A-BF99-DAA8998BE69F" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-9AF3C1DE-12C0-43D5-BA44-B7AFFBF1E958-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-9AF3C1DE-12C0-43D5-BA44-B7AFFBF1E958-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">5 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Remove the 3 screws. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-97164726-E490-470F-84E4-59043C95529F" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-E46EEDCC-C643-498B-B69E-2C8776B5CF6D-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-E46EEDCC-C643-498B-B69E-2C8776B5CF6D-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-5ED14E76-9CB6-4E5B-96CD-B36557256870" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-940904EC-3D34-47C2-A3E4-4B549B2953DB-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-940904EC-3D34-47C2-A3E4-4B549B2953DB-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">6 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Slide the assembly from the frame (Opposite direction of the yellow arrows). 
</p><note id="GUID-A0394BF8-E3ED-4A9B-A005-80552073A5DC" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">Location plastic cover 
</p><fig id="GUID-AD7F5B19-454E-48C7-A6AC-5AB3B1180C69" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-4616BA8D-B02D-4BDD-9A83-6C979A209544-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-4616BA8D-B02D-4BDD-9A83-6C979A209544-low.png"/></fig></note></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-1620C22F-543C-44E9-A70F-F44A6A5E1342" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-3BB01658-A448-49F2-AB92-270E3C9083B2-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-3BB01658-A448-49F2-AB92-270E3C9083B2-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-58B14B75-48AF-47BF-84F2-F621F1232925" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-50B844B3-E437-4D85-9B97-934C483E3F43-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-50B844B3-E437-4D85-9B97-934C483E3F43-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-C80C79A8-3CA7-4859-8B10-4FBFB6A28499" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-DBEB9FCD-AA66-41A7-A521-602F31E9EC5F-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-DBEB9FCD-AA66-41A7-A521-602F31E9EC5F-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-E26F9F43-1CB5-4DD2-86ED-4C7AF741D32D" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-624E699E-AD8B-4114-A032-F6B6F1761D8A-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-624E699E-AD8B-4114-A032-F6B6F1761D8A-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">7 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Loosen the 2 x 3 screws. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-9331C5AA-4D19-4811-A8E3-B1D260C0A432" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-538E840D-F91C-4DC6-A853-FA4A3216D3F4-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-538E840D-F91C-4DC6-A853-FA4A3216D3F4-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">8 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Remove the spring of the motor. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-305F0800-E24F-443E-A19B-010DAEA38E64" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-E2C3CD1D-BAA3-4BF5-8B36-24B4B477223A-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-E2C3CD1D-BAA3-4BF5-8B36-24B4B477223A-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">9 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the drive belt from the motor. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-B435CF4E-7D42-438C-B774-ACB7EBD12BD6" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-402ED2C9-0AD3-4CDA-825F-D4B1C5A00519-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-402ED2C9-0AD3-4CDA-825F-D4B1C5A00519-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">10 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Remove the 2 springs. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-EA6D3618-875F-4EF4-BD35-34CA929ACB83" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-19961C49-554C-4E29-84EF-FD94B4F2154E-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-19961C49-554C-4E29-84EF-FD94B4F2154E-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-54F6B245-4620-432E-A9DC-57F16290180A" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-526FDF58-E6BC-4AB0-93FD-7E3B212EEBF3-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-526FDF58-E6BC-4AB0-93FD-7E3B212EEBF3-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">11 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Remove the 5 nuts. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-48C8CDA9-924C-4EC1-93F2-78132F5F4732" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-BFCA84A0-EAEF-42C7-A145-B47919CAB65E-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-BFCA84A0-EAEF-42C7-A145-B47919CAB65E-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">12 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Take the drive assembly out of the frame. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-91B414A2-906D-4149-B960-B77BD75E545B" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-93B3CE7E-B58B-4089-AC1E-D157AFBC1C70-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-93B3CE7E-B58B-4089-AC1E-D157AFBC1C70-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">13 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the drive belt. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-DE364AC3-8F9A-4F50-856D-AFE450046AAF" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-ED614EFF-4A0C-42B8-8555-49650FEB7B46-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-ED614EFF-4A0C-42B8-8555-49650FEB7B46-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">14 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the gear. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-147CE855-7AE8-4936-B4B2-BA06CA23DB69" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-FFA7DF7C-01DE-4CD9-96A1-0DC1B464AB37-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-FFA7DF7C-01DE-4CD9-96A1-0DC1B464AB37-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">15 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the spring ring. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-9BE9B00E-B4D1-47AC-AFA2-C846A1123AF5" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-A13D0686-6EFA-4E23-B5A4-3A92F5DA1FB9-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-A13D0686-6EFA-4E23-B5A4-3A92F5DA1FB9-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">16 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the drive belt. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-770F1B49-F412-452D-A3A4-659DA995EE61" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-A4B0D1B5-480B-44A3-BD3B-8651784AB210-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-A4B0D1B5-480B-44A3-BD3B-8651784AB210-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">17 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the gear. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-7B73AFB5-8A0A-4A5B-A3B6-C57BA31229EE" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-30B885BB-0629-4AB7-BA78-28CC208E1281-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-30B885BB-0629-4AB7-BA78-28CC208E1281-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">18 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the spring ring. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-E855AB31-1EFE-481C-BE77-905ACBDC3817" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-810E7BFE-D819-4BC1-A5B7-70FAF1C7B654-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-810E7BFE-D819-4BC1-A5B7-70FAF1C7B654-low.png"/></fig></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section><section id="GUID-234D70A5-41EC-40E2-9E43-4217D346F540" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">How to install</title><table pgwide="1" id="TABLE_F77204E29D3E4F6D8F3503958683C72F" class="- topic/table "><tgroup align="left" outputclass="step" cols="3" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="10*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="50*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col3" colnum="3" colwidth="40*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead valign="top" class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Step 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remarks 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody valign="top" class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">1 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Install in reverse order. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> 
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">2 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Reconnect the Service jumper, exit SDS and press 'Restart' on the operator panel. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section></taskbody><related-links class="- topic/related-links "><linkpool class="- topic/linkpool " mapkeyref="GUID-8A41CFEA-5928-4042-A2CB-507A5D034160"><link class="- topic/link " mapclass="- map/topicref " format="dita" type="concept" href="generated-topic-GUID-8D3A1F62-9497-4853-8507-1AEACBF21ABC.xml" role="parent"><?ditaot usertext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext "><?ditaot usertext?>Dis-assembly</linktext></link></linkpool></related-links>
</task>